        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You study magic at the Arcanamirium on Absalom Station, one of Dykon's or Pabaq's universities, or somewhere else. You might be a novice still learning the basics of magic while enjoying university life or an opinionated professor researching a niche subject.</p>\n<p>Choose two attribute boosts. One must be to <strong>Intelligence</strong> or <strong>Wisdom</strong>, and one is a free attribute boost.</p>\n<p>You're trained in your choice of the Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion skill, based on your primary field of study, and the Academia Lore skill. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Quick Identification] skill feat.</p>"
